reviewText:
My toddler loves this DVD and all the songs on it. We watch or listen to it almost daily.
The Wiggles take on several musical genres with hits like 1960's pop sounding "The Wonder of Wiggle Town," Classic Country styled "Gymkana Yodel," Discoesque "Do The Pretzel," and the early 20th Century hit "On the Sidewalks of New York." Every song is upbeat and catchy enough for all family members to sing along.
This is sure to become an instant hit with your family!
I loved it it was very Awesome !!
My special needs daughter loves Wiggles
Fun songs bright colors. The baby loves the wiggles,  and watching this one over and over hasn't driven us parents crazy yet.
My 10 month old and 4 year old grandsons love this DVD.  I do too. Several catchy tunes.
Fantastic album, great house pacifier...top favorite is the very catchy Irish Stew has the kids dancing around the house.
Another great Wiggles dvd...one of my son's favorites, along with "Wiggly Halloween" and "Rock n' Roll Preschool".  My son is a ten year old with Autism.  These dvds are a lifesaver!
My daughter is wiggles obsessed. She has loved every movie she has seen and this one is no different. I look forward to the new movies as well so we can give the old ones a rest!
